HEADWORD: Metachrosis
<hw>Met`a*chro"sis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., from
Gr. <?/ beyond + <?/ a coloring.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>The
